The last I heard was that the PC port of Essence was on indefinite hold.
Apex is probably very busy porting Essence textures to LW4.0. The complaint
they made about IM30-PC was the difficulty in getting the standards from
Impulse.

The point about IM31 having more than enough great textures is a good one.
The reason we might like to see Essence on the PC (from the Amiga standpoint)
is for compatibility. I believe both versions should have much the same support
from 3rd party as well as from Impulse.

Doug Rudd
